# Editorial Policy

_Last Updated: July 2026_

At **Senkai World**, our goal is to provide accurate, engaging, and trustworthy content for anime and manhwa fans around the world. We are committed to maintaining high editorial standards across every article we publish.

## Our Content

We publish content related to:

- Anime news
- Manhwa news
- Anime reviews
- Manhwa recommendations
- Rankings and lists
- Release updates
- Guides and features

Our content is created to inform, entertain, and help readers discover great series.

## Accuracy

We strive to ensure that all information is accurate at the time of publication. News articles are based on official announcements whenever possible, while reviews and rankings reflect editorial opinions.

If new information becomes available, we update our articles to keep them accurate and relevant.

## Editorial Independence

Our opinions and recommendations are created independently. Advertisers or third parties do not influence our editorial decisions.

## Corrections

If you notice factual errors or outdated information, please contact us at:

**senkaiworld.in@gmail.com**

We review all correction requests and update articles when necessary.

